Stored in Kunlun (ask: Xiaodong, Liang Xiao, JiaCheng Ding)

download from: https://www.cosmosim.org/metadata/bigmdpl/
path:  /home/xiaodongli/data/BigMDPL 

csvs/BigMDPL_mge1e13.csv:  halo/subhalo at all snapshots with M>1e13 MSolar

lightcone/: a lightcone mock for SDSS BOSS DR12, see https://arxiv.org/abs/1607.03155

z0/: snapshot halo/subhalo at z=0

snaps/: all snapshot halo/subhalo
  Redshifts.csv : redshift - SnapId relation
  1.csv, 2.csv, ..., 79.csv: catalogue
  *.shiftx, *.shifty, *.shiftz: RSD added along x/y/z axies
  nbar1e-3/: nbar=1e-3, by applying a mass threshold
    examples of some 2pcf files:
      79_nbar1e-3.shiftr.om0.3071_w-1.0000.radeczw.150s0to150.120mu.2pcf:
        2pcf measured at snapid=79, RSD added along r direction
      79_nbar1e-3.shiftz.numNB30.margin30.00.boxsize2500.00.zplus1000000000.weipow0.3.150s0to150.120mu.2pcf
        mark weighted 2pcf measured at snapid=79, RSD added along z direction, weighted by rho^0.3, rho estimated using 30 neighbors
        
       
  
